</P>
<P>
 * Shari Lewis & Lamb Chop, Feb. 11 
</P>
<P>
 * Theatre Sans Fil, of Toronto, with "The Dream Catchers," Feb. 25, 26 
</P>
<P>
 * The Cerritos Center for the Performing Arts is at 12700 Center Court Drive, 
Cerritos. Tickets to all shows will go on sale via mail and fax (310-916-8514) 
at noon on June 25. Phone and walk-up service will begin July 5. (310) 916-8500 
or (800) 300-4345. ZAN DUBIN 
</P>
