<P>
AFTERSHOCK WATCH 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 No Northridge earthquake aftershocks greater than magnitude 3.0 were recorded 
between 8 p.m. Wednesday and 8 p.m. Thursday, according to Caltech. 
</P>
</TEXT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA060394-0179 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 047956 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
June 3, 1994, Friday, Valley Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Metro; Part B; Page 1; Column 2 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
