</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Olmos endorsement -- Based on information provided by the gubernatorial 
campaign of state Sen. Tom Hayden, The Times on Sunday incorrectly listed actor 
Edward James Olmos as a Hayden supporter. Daniel Haro, community relations 
director for Olmos Productions, said that although Olmos and Hayden may agree 
on some issues, Olmos never endorses political candidates. 
</P>
